[h1]The background-color Property[/h1]

The [b]background-color[/b] property is used to specify the background color of an element. 

[b]The HTML:[/b][code format="html" ]<p>The background color of this page is set to LightSkyBlue.</p>[/code]
[b]The CSS:[/b][code format="css" codeId="544"]body {
    [b]background-color[/b]: #87CEFA;
}[/code]
[b]Result:[/b] [img id="2624" width="100%"]

