quizzes.textContent:
[h1]The Background Color Values[/h1]

The color of the background can be defined using three different formats: a [b]color name[/b], [b]hexadecimal values[/b], and [b]RGB[/b]. 

In the example below, the body, h1, and p elements are assigned different background colors: 

[b]The HTML:[/b][code format="html" ]<h1>This is a heading</h1>
<p>This is a paragraph</p>[/code]
[b]The CSS:[/b][code format="css" codeId="545"]body {
   background-color: [b]#C0C0C0[/b];
}
h1 {
   background-color: [b]rgb(135,206,235)[/b];
}
p {
   background-color: [b]LightGreen[/b];
}[/code]
[b]Result:[/b] [img id="2625" width="100%"]
